  <section xml:lang="en" title="DuEPublico: Duisburg-Essen Publications online">
  
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-body text-white bg-info">
        DuEPublico is the institutional repository of the University of Duisburg-Essen.
        Currently, the <a style="color:white; text-decoration:underline" href="https://duepublico.uni-duisburg-essen.de">old</a> and new
        version of our repository are running in parallel.
        Here on DuEPublico 2 you currently find
        <strong>all electronic thesis and dissertations, Open Educational Resources</strong>
        as well as <strong>Open Access publications</strong> including full text.
        Certain series and journals, video lectures as well as further learning material 
        currently still can be accessed 
        <a style="color:white; text-decoration:underline" href="https://duepublico.uni-duisburg-essen.de">via the old server</a>.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <h3 class="card-title">
          <i class="fas fa-file-alt" style="margin-right:0.5ex;" aria-hidden="true" />
          Open Access E-Publications
        </h3>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body" style="hyphens:auto;">
        <img src="../images/openaccess.png" alt="Open Access Logo" class="img-fluid float-right" />
        <p>
          University members may publish their works online.
          Your primary or secondary publications will be made citeable by assigning an Digital Object Identifier (DOI),
          recording them at the German National Library
          and making the available world-wide in the sense of Open Access.        </p>
        <p>
          Here on DuEPublico 2 you can already find
          <a href="../servlets/solr/select?q=objectType%3Amods+AND+state%3Apublished+AND+category%3A%22collection%3APub%22&amp;fl=*&amp;sort=mods.dateIssued+desc&amp;rows=20">many current Open Access publications</a>.
          We are continuously moving all contens from the old to the new system.
          To
          <a href="https://duepublico.uni-duisburg-essen.de/authoring/openaccess.xml">publish your new works</a>
          please for now still use the form on the old server.
          There you will also find
          <a href="https://duepublico.uni-duisburg-essen.de/authoring/openaccess.xml">works that have been published so far</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

